                            <h5 style="font-weight: bold;">06/06/2021: H.E The President's latest address on the second wave of COVID-19 </h5>
                            <div>
                                <iframe width="100%" height="360" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/fd-HJJQOWvU" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen></iframe> 
